latestIgtvVideos.title: @grwmcosmetics #grwmgoalgettersclub ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I’ve always been insecure about what other people might think about me. I bet it came from the times that I got bullied in school and that one time I saw someone on tv being so conscious about literally everything. 

Growing up in a world where beauty standards was all about being perfect I didn’t know where I would fit in—I was so lost (being a petite, hormonal teen and all). I knew I needed to do something about it.

I kept my my head held high, found a creative outlet(beauty, of course!), and stuck with the people who truly got my back—you know who you are! 🥺

Now more than ever, I feel empowered just by the thought of me taking control of my life and finding my purpose. There are so many women playing important roles in society and they’ve acted as huge inspirations. Because of them, I’m constantly challenging myself to be better so I can also empower others. 

That’s the true #goalgetter spirit!🤍

#grwmgoalgettersclub #grwmcosmetics @grwmcosmetics @maealayug #grwm
